ResourceHeader.ResourceName: Ulysses Heliosphere Instrument for Spectral, Composition, and Anisotropy at Low Energies (HISCALE) LEFS150 MFSA, Solar Wind Frame, Sectored Electron Fluxes, Daily Averages

RevisionEvent.Note: Only known prior ReleaseDate of the metadata

Added MetadataRightsList. Added ResourceType and NamingAuthority. Updated to 2.7.1. Changed http to https in top-level schemaLocation attribute. Fixed version number separator in top-level schemaLocation attribute. ZCB

ResourceHeader.Description: Daily-averaged sectored electron fluxes from the MF Spectrum Analyzer of the Ulysses/HISCALE LEFS150 instrument. All energies thresholds take into account the incident particle type, shielding, and inactive dead-layer of the solid state detector. All fluxes are background corrected and are in the solar wind rest frame.
